# Designs

## Chat-D1 GateCard & SecretaryMessage Components
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/components/`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-A1, Chat-A1

```typescript
// GateCard.vue
interface GateCardProps {
  gate: PendingGate
  mode: 'inline' | 'secretary'
}

// SecretaryMessage.vue
interface SecretaryMessageProps {
  gate: PendingGate
  queuePosition?: number
}
```

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Proposed
    Proposed --> Approved : boss clicks Approve
    Proposed --> Rejected : boss clicks Reject
    Proposed --> Snoozed : boss clicks Snooze
    Proposed --> Reviewing : boss clicks Review →
    Reviewing --> Proposed : drawer closed
    Snoozed --> Proposed : timer expires
    Approved --> Resolved : auto-collapse 3s
    Rejected --> Resolved : advisor reworks
    Resolved --> [*]
```

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `gate.id` | `string` | session_id or run_id |
| `gate.type` | `'session' \| 'run'` | source composable |
| `gate.gateType` | `'goal' \| 'spec' \| 'review'` | approval type |
| `gate.profession` | `string` | who is waiting |
| `gate.since` | `number` | timestamp |


