## Chat-D2 ReportCard (Chat Terminal)
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/components/ReportCard.vue`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-A1

```typescript
interface ReportCardProps {
  report: {
    runId: string
    goalsMet: string
    testsPass: string
    driftDetected: string
    cost: string
    confidence: 'High' | 'Medium' | 'Low'
    deliverables: string[]
  }
}
```

- `collapsed` (default): Shows summary line only — "✅ Relay Complete — Report X42"
- `expanded`: Shows full metrics table, cost breakdown, deliverables list, drift notes

- [View Full Report] → opens Reports section in Specs drawer
- [Download Markdown] → triggers download of report markdown
- [Open Changed Files] → opens file diff viewer


